{"tid":2394080,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(拜登概念股) SAVA","createTime":"2021-02-04T02:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T15:45:16.000Z","uid":3661,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"fb16418b288155fe4e555e6d167dbdc5ba8118f9","tid":2394080,"uid":3661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T02:44:38.000Z","msg":"Cassava Sciences, Inc.(<a href=\"http://SAVA.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FSAVA.US&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZREXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=0063e95b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">SAVA.US</a>)前身為Pain Therapeutics, Inc.，2019年3月更為現名，成立於1998年，總部位於美國德州奧斯丁，在美國開發用於神經系統疾病的藥物，其開發中的FENROCK為專利的防濫用經皮疼痛貼片，用於緩解疼痛；PTI-125為治療阿茲海默症的小分子候選藥物；PTI-125DX為檢測阿茲海默症的血液診斷/生物標記。<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nShares of Cassava Sciences jumped another 10% in Wednesday&rsquo;s pre-market session (3/2/2021) after more than doubling yesterday, as the small-cap biotech company released promising results from an interim study of its lead investigational drug, sumifilam, for the treatment of Alzheimer's disease (AD).<br />\n<br />\nCassava Sciences (SAVA) said that the study showed that patient cognition and behavior scores both improved following six months of treatment with simufilam. No safety issues were encountered. The biotech company noted that cognition of individuals suffering from Alzheimer&rsquo;s disease will always worsen as the illness is a progressive one.<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n現價 $87.95, 盤後$121.6,差不多100% growth<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴打有留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7e730fd5bebf93a99fa853bcf286780ca405bc","tid":2394080,"uid":204163,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:42:57.000Z","msg":"關拜登咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2855c8bb412d5a05c5a857b73408b3790abdd5e9","tid":2394080,"uid":3661,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"quote":{"pid":"4a7e730fd5bebf93a99fa853bcf286780ca405bc","tid":2394080,"uid":204163,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:42:57.000Z","msg":"關拜登咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"老人痴呆藥"},{"pid":"a783e6e4e1124c64565b9bbb7d70ccbb37b304fd","tid":2394080,"uid":204163,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2855c8bb412d5a05c5a857b73408b3790abdd5e9","tid":2394080,"uid":3661,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"quote":{"pid":"4a7e730fd5bebf93a99fa853bcf286780ca405bc","tid":2394080,"uid":204163,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:42:57.000Z","msg":"關拜登咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"老人痴呆藥"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />OK<br />\n做咩突然升得咁勁，ching睇幾多?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548d24181e116f4ed5723191e959e6b85d167b0a","tid":2394080,"uid":3661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a783e6e4e1124c64565b9bbb7d70ccbb37b304fd","tid":2394080,"uid":204163,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2855c8bb412d5a05c5a857b73408b3790abdd5e9","tid":2394080,"uid":3661,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"quote":{"pid":"4a7e730fd5bebf93a99fa853bcf286780ca405bc","tid":2394080,"uid":204163,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03: